#include <iostream>

using namespace std;

int main()
{
    int t;
    cin >> t;
    while (t--) {
        int x1,y1,x2,y2,x4,y4,x5,y5;
        cin >> x1 >> y1 >> x2 >> y2 >> x4 >> y4 >> x5 >> y5;
        if (x1 <= x4 && x4 <= x2 && y4 <= y1 && y1 <= y5)
            cout << x4 << " " << y1 << " " << x2 << " " << y5 << endl;
        else
            cout << "No Overlap" << endl;
    }
    return 0;
}
